menuconfig LVGL_DISPLAY
	bool "LVGL graphical weather-station display"
	depends on LVGL && DISPLAY && ZBUS && SENSOR_EVENT && ZBUS_RUNTIME_OBSERVERS
	help
	  SDL-backed 320x240 window showing the weather-station title, a large
	  HH:MM clock (updated from SYS_CLOCK_REALTIME), and the last reading per
	  sensor UID/type pair. Subscribes to sensor_event_chan via a zbus
	  listener; uses lv_async_call() for thread-safe LVGL widget updates.
	  SYS_INIT at APPLICATION priority 91 (after LVGL workqueue at 90).
